OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, mostly light, but
OL,8,Fperhaps briefly moderate or heavy for
OL,9,Fa time. Mist or fog patches developing
OL,10,Faround western coasts later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,13,Fspots of light rain, but some drier,
OL,14,Fbrighter spells developing in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Outbreaks of rain will then
OL,16,Fspread northeast during the evening
OL,17,Fand overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
